public final class GL11 extends GL11C
GL11 relies on preview features of the Java platform:
  • GL11 refers to one or more preview APIs: MemorySegment, SegmentAllocator.
Programs can only use GL11 when preview features are enabled.
Preview features may be removed in a future release, or upgraded to permanent features of the Java platform.
The OpenGL 1.1 functions.
